item.title: PE Stretch Film
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
our productPE stretch film warp

Stretch film pallet wrap, is an LLDPE plastic film with high elastic recovery used to wrap and unitized pallets for load stability and protection.

There are many different stretch films on the market today.
What differentiates films are their characteristics to provide.

the necessary degree of load stability to deliver the pallet as you intend reducing film usage and ultimately the cost of film per delivered load.

Technical Data Watch Video

Clipsico Pack supplies the most reliable and consistent range of stretch films in various sizes & thicknesses.

350% pre-stretch
and Light Weight System High
transparency and clarity Great tear and puncture resistance Great
strength and durability

Our products have various means of application

To meet all your packaging needs, Clipsico Pack provides the widest possible collection of PE Stretch Films. We provide multilayer wrap film with high quality by different means of applications:

  • Manual stretch film
  • Automatic stretch film
  • Power stretch film
  • Super power stretch film

7 LAYER STRUCTURE OF STRETCH FILM

The multilayer structure of stretch film provides an opportunity to make a film with certain physical and mechanical properties and the adhesive side of the web. The material of each layer of the film are different brands of linear low density polyethylene (LLDPE).

cilpsicopack

offers a wide range of high-performance stretch wrap

request an inquiry How to achieve lowest total cost

Downgauging your stretch film saves not only money but also the environment.

Read More

With right gauging

" The thickness of a roll of stretch film is commonly known as its gauge. Gauge, or mil thickness, is indicated by a number “

Converting from standard stretch film to power stretch film

“is our answer to rising machine stretch film costs”

UVI stretch film and Colored stretch film

1. Detours pilferage through valuable shipments by concealing products.
2. It helps to protect products from UV Rays.
3. Prevents damage caused by rain, dew, and dust.
4. Outlasts regular transparent stretch film during extended outdoor storage.
5. Great for color-coding products.

request an inquiry Stretch film can be recyclable

Stretch film wrap for pallets can be recycled , which means you can make an impact by going green. The bottom line is that stretch film has many benefits for your business when it comes to wrapping a pallet securely and can have a positive impact on the environment Contact Clipsico packaging supply for more information on stretch film options for your business

item.title: Quality
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
packagingquality

Packaging quality control is the process of ensuring that your products are properly protected during shipping and storage.

This includes everything from the quality of the materials used to building the packaging to how the product is packaged and shipped.

Our Certificate Explore Ourquality

"Our value starts and never ends at providing the best services in the field of packaging materials. We strive for market leadership and the care of maintaining a competitive edge, to remain nimble in everyday operation."

Best Customer Service

We guarantee customer satisfaction at the different levels of the operation, through timely delivery of quality products within an environment of continuous improvement.

Personal Development

We take pride in the principled, responsible and lawful manner in which we conduct ourselves and our business. We recognize the fact that best organizations comprised of the best people - employees who are adaptable, engaged and eager to learn. 

Passionate Team

Attracting, maintaining, and motivating a talented staff will position Clipsico Pack at the top of our services. We accomplish this by encouraging respect and compassion, personnel knowledge growth, and embracing diversity within our workplace.

Code of Conducts

" Clipsico Pack is totally committed to produce and deliver our services with focus on quality, performance, innovation and customer satisfaction through our code of conducts. Clipisco Pack team is expected to embrace the principles of our Code ."

Customer Focus

When dealing with our customers, Clipsico Pack always earns their business on the basis of superior products,customer service and competitive price.

We understand the requirements of customers and work to develop and improve all aspects of our business.

Health & Safety

We at Clipsico Pack shall always do everything possible to ensure the safety of each employee and to maintain and improve.

The workplace environment so that we can work in a safe and healthy surrounding.

Confidently

We shall protect customers' privacy and not to disclose any information obtained in.

The workplace or during business operations.

Involvement of People

Promoting culture of continuous learning & training, participation & involvement of people at all levels of our business.

Continuous Improvements & Quality

By continuously establishing and improving the effectiveness of our quality, Clipsico Pack is committed to producing high quality products.

Achieving operational excellence by better productivity and driving continual improvements of our products, processes, systems, and services.

Responsibility Towards the Environment

Clipsico Pack shall always protect the environment within which it operates.

We tend to minimize the environmental impact at all times as we engage in our day-to-day work and to prevent waste of natural resources.

item.title: Quality
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
packagingquality

Packaging quality control is the process of ensuring that your products are properly protected during shipping and storage.

This includes everything from the quality of the materials used to building the packaging to how the product is packaged and shipped.

Our Certificate Explore Ourquality

"Our value starts and never ends at providing the best services in the field of packaging materials. We strive for market leadership and the care of maintaining a competitive edge, to remain nimble in everyday operation."

Best Customer Service

We guarantee customer satisfaction at the different levels of the operation, through timely delivery of quality products within an environment of continuous improvement.

Personal Development

We take pride in the principled, responsible and lawful manner in which we conduct ourselves and our business. We recognize the fact that best organizations comprised of the best people - employees who are adaptable, engaged and eager to learn. 

Passionate Team

Attracting, maintaining, and motivating a talented staff will position Clipsico Pack at the top of our services. We accomplish this by encouraging respect and compassion, personnel knowledge growth, and embracing diversity within our workplace.

Part & Full Loads Personal Development Passionate Team

Code of Conducts

" Clipsico Pack is totally committed to produce and deliver our services with focus on quality, performance, innovation and customer satisfaction through our code of conducts. Clipisco Pack team is expected to embrace the principles of our Code ."

Customer Focus

When dealing with our customers, Clipsico Pack always earns their business on the basis of superior products,customer service and competitive price.

We understand the requirements of customers and work to develop and improve all aspects of our business.

Health & Safety

We at Clipsico Pack shall always do everything possible to ensure the safety of each employee and to maintain and improve.

The workplace environment so that we can work in a safe and healthy surrounding.

Confidently

We shall protect customers' privacy and not to disclose any information obtained in.

The workplace or during business operations.

Involvement of People

Promoting culture of continuous learning & training, participation & involvement of people at all levels of our business.

Continuous Improvements & Quality

By continuously establishing and improving the effectiveness of our quality, Clipsico Pack is committed to producing high quality products.

Achieving operational excellence by better productivity and driving continual improvements of our products, processes, systems, and services.

Responsibility Towards the Environment

Clipsico Pack shall always protect the environment within which it operates.

We tend to minimize the environmental impact at all times as we engage in our day-to-day work and to prevent waste of natural resources.

item.title: Quality
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
packagingquality

Packaging quality control is the process of ensuring that your products are properly protected during shipping and storage.

This includes everything from the quality of the materials used to building the packaging to how the product is packaged and shipped.

Our Certificate Explore Ourquality

"Our value starts and never ends at providing the best services in the field of packaging materials. We strive for market leadership and the care of maintaining a competitive edge, to remain nimble in everyday operation."

Best Customer Service

We guarantee customer satisfaction at the different levels of the operation, through timely delivery of quality products within an environment of continuous improvement.

Personal Development

We take pride in the principled, responsible and lawful manner in which we conduct ourselves and our business. We recognize the fact that best organizations comprised of the best people - employees who are adaptable, engaged and eager to learn. 

Passionate Team

Attracting, maintaining, and motivating a talented staff will position Clipsico Pack at the top of our services. We accomplish this by encouraging respect and compassion, personnel knowledge growth, and embracing diversity within our workplace.

Part & Full Loads Personal Development Passionate Team

Code of Conducts

" Clipsico Pack is totally committed to produce and deliver our services with focus on quality, performance, innovation and customer satisfaction through our code of conducts. Clipisco Pack team is expected to embrace the principles of our Code ."

Customer Focus

When dealing with our customers, Clipsico Pack always earns their business on the basis of superior products,customer service and competitive price.

We understand the requirements of customers and work to develop and improve all aspects of our business.

Health & Safety

We at Clipsico Pack shall always do everything possible to ensure the safety of each employee and to maintain and improve.

The workplace environment so that we can work in a safe and healthy surrounding.

Confidently

We shall protect customers' privacy and not to disclose any information obtained in.

The workplace or during business operations.

Involvement of People

Promoting culture of continuous learning & training, participation & involvement of people at all levels of our business.

Continuous Improvements & Quality

By continuously establishing and improving the effectiveness of our quality, Clipsico Pack is committed to producing high quality products.

Achieving operational excellence by better productivity and driving continual improvements of our products, processes, systems, and services.

Responsibility Towards the Environment

Clipsico Pack shall always protect the environment within which it operates.

item.title: Word of CEO
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
Explore Ourword of ceo

Clipsico Pack’s long term vision is to become the leading manufacturer and supplier of packaging and wrapping solutions. Our excellence in operation, which is based on quality, is what defines our production process. We incorporate quality into our production in order to generate project and product excellence. We strive to exceed customers’ expectations and meet the variations in their demands.

As a socially and environmentally responsible PP (Polypropylene) strap & LLDPE (Linear Low Density Polyethylene) stretch film manufacturer, we are committed to provide high quality products and conduct our manufacturing operations within the prescribed environmental policies and guidelines. We advocate for a safer environment at the work place to reduce hazardous and accidental rates.

With a solid foundation and a visionary management, we are highly-motivated to produce sustainable packaging solutions. As the packaging industry will relentlessly grow, we will continue upgrading our products with smart shapes, space saving packaging, reduction in packaging materials, better recycling and biodegradable packaging

We are an organized, innovative and trustworthy packaging partner. Our position cannot be easily attained without the dedicated hard work and teamwork collaboration among our customers, employees and business partners. With the dedication and experience of our people we will continue to grow and successfully achieve our goals. We look forward to your continuous support and to deliver good quality products and services to benefit all parties together.

item.title: How can the quality of LLDPE affects the Stretch film?
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
High quality of raw material affects the stretch film quality

The higher the quality of PE material the more transparency you will obviously see and the better quality too.

The better quality of polyethylene in production can make it stretch from 150%, 250 %, and 300 %.

We also recognize the importance of ISO in establishing global standards and the need for certification. We ensure our Global Product Quality Management System (GPQMS) is ISO9001:2015.

With Clipsico pack ,

item.title: Our Company
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
clipsico Pack is One of the Leading Manufacturers

Clipsico Pack is one of the remarkable manufacturers and suppliers of industrial packaging materials in Egypt .

Our business is related to packaging industry, we specifically deal in wrapping material, strapping material, adhesive tapes and more.

We offer our clients with high standards and quality products in innovative packaging solutions .

Clipsico Pack is dedicated to provide the clients with quick, courteous and responsive service. At a timely manner, we provide excellent support at the best price.

View Products

Best Quality, Affordable price

We offer our clients standards and quality products

We are committed to providing customers with prompt service

We provide excellent support at the best price.

Explore Our history

Having been established in Alexandria, Egypt since 1986, Clipsico Pack has progressed to a great position in the market. Clipsico Pack has grown dealing in the packaging materials business, as a supplier and exporter to many packaging solutions as PP straps and PE stretch films.

  1. 1986
  2. 1989
  3. 1992
  4. 1994
  5. 1996
  6. 1998
  7. 2004
  8. 2006
  9. 2007
  10. 2009
  11. 2012
  12. 2014
  13. 2015
  14. 2020
  15. 2022
  1. Clipsicopack is founded in Alexandria, Egypt, starting with steel buckles production
  2. Begin trading of PP straps
  3. Start first production line of PP manual strap
  4. Building new plant with new two other production lines of PP strap
  5. Prime manufacturer and supplier of manual PP straps and buckles in Egypt
  6. Open new corporate headquarter in Alexandria, importing packaging consumables
  7. Start trading of food & industrial PE stretch film
  8. Importing raw materials, starting
  9. Start production line of PE wrapping multi-layer stretch films
  10. Start exporting process
  11. New production line of Automatic PP straps
  12. Beginning production line of PET strap
  13. Become one of the most important packaging suppliers in Egypt, packaging materials sole supplier for giant Egyptian enterprises
  14. Increase PE stretch film production capacity, new manufacturing site of high performance multi-layers polyethene stretch film
  15. Clipsico pack has expanded its export sales to 70% to new markets .

Explore Our Mission & Vision

Every day at Clipsico pack, one idea leads to the next, igniting the momentum that has made us an industry leader. Simply put, we are a team of engineers, professional problem solvers, innovators, and perfectionists, working around the clock to be the best flexible packaging manufacturer in the industry

Our mission

Our stability, innovation and customizable services attract large firms and small business alike. Demanding to always be a trusted partner .

We aspire to be a customer-oriented, market-led company where the satisfaction of customers is seen as being essential as from the aim of creating the ultimate value .

To fulfill their expectations rapidly, reliably and cost effectively and to build partnerships based on trust and mutual success.

our vision

Clipsico Pack target tomorrow’s excellence to be a global company that shapes the future of packaging industry. To be the top-tier,

We will persistently spearhead the development of customized and differentiated packaging solutions for a fast moving operation.

Our values gives us a shared, unifying ambition, we are committed to those values, it shapes our role and purpose .

item.title: Environmental Responsibility
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
developmentOur environmental responsibility

Clipsico pack is committed to acting in an environmentally responsible manner. We work hard to reduce the impact on the environment by making a few steps towards a greener environment.

To achieve this result, we ensure our products and operations and services comply with relevant environmental legislation and regulations. We ensure that materials are properly stored, reducing use of hazardous materials and recycling waste. We will also ensure that all residual waste are properly stored and disposed.

Our company implements its environmental policy both internally to its employees, as well as externally to its suppliers, customers and visitors.

item.title: Corporate Responsibility
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
Our corporate responsibility

One of our great advantages is our CEO’s leading ability and our firm’s belief in the training and development of our team and following up the strategy that always keeps us focused on the same organizational goal, It also makes our organization proactive.

The connection and commitment employees exhibit towards the organization leads to higher levels of productive work behaviors and makes them actively committed to their role in achieving our organizational goals.

Our company implements its environmental policy both internally to its employees, as well as externally to its suppliers, customers and visitors.

So what are the benefits?
  • Improving employee performance
  • Improving employee satisfaction and morale
  • Addressing our firm weaknesses
  • Enhancing company reputation and profile
  • Reducing employee turnover
  •  Firm Consistency
  • Increasing productivity and adherence to quality standards
  • Increasing innovation in new strategies and products

item.title: Lower Cost Stretch Film
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
our productWith right gauging

The thickness of a roll of stretch film is commonly known as its gauge. Gauge, or mil thickness, is indicated by a number. In the past, the idea was that the higher the number

The stronger the film , but you can now buy thinner films that work just as well as traditional higher gauge films. And, these thinner films will cost you less money

This simple action can save your business money on stretch wrapping. In fact, it can save your business a ton of money (on average, we are talking a savings of 15 – 30%) on each and every wrapped load.

Watch Video Who Can Help You To Downgauge Your Stretch Film?

If you want to find out if downgauging your stretch wrap is the right choice for your product palletizing and containment needs, you will want to consider talking with a packaging specialist

Contact Us

converting from standard stretch film to power stretch film

Is our answer to rising machine stretch film costs. The performance stretch film is a multi-layered machine stretch film that provides more stretch than traditional machine stretch film. It offers a high amount of cling and downsizing opportunity.

Watch Video

our productPolypropylene strapping

Is used in different segments of industries due to its economic and simplicity in operations. It is used to secure items for shipping or storage.

Technical Data Watch Video 01manual Is issued in a simple method for tightening strapping around a load. They save time and are easily applied. Manual PP Strap ensures that loads are safely tightened during transit, handling, and storage. 02automatic Is issued in a simple method for tightening strapping around a load. They save time and are easily applied. Manual PP Strap ensures that loads are safely tightened during transit, handling, and storage. 03semi-automatic Is issued in a simple method for tightening strapping around a load. They save time and are easily applied. Manual PP Strap ensures that loads are safely tightened during transit, handling, and storage. cilpsicopack

offers wide range of high performance stretch wrap

request an inquiry Key features of PP Straps
  • High-speed application.
  • Optimal security.
  • High tear durability.
  • Resistance against moisture.
  • Adaptation to the form of the packed object.
  • Elongation 10 – 25%.
  • Safety sealing of products for transport.
  • Colored (white, black, yellow, red, blue, and green).

item.title: PET Strap
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
our productPolyester strapping

Is used when regular polypropylene strapping isn’t strong enough to get the job done. Polyester strap most closely resembles steel strapping in its physical characteristics.

Polyester strapping will withstand higher tensioning than other plastic strapping up to 25% higher, with equivalent break strengths. It will retain tension on rigid loads better than other non-metallic strapping.

Quality’s polyester strapping is virtually unaffected by weather or ultraviolet rays. It is significantly lower in cost than steel strapping, a lot safer to use, and easier to dispose of too.

Just imagine how to get rid of steel strapping waste? Polyester strapping is also much safer to use than metal strapping since it has no sharp edges.

Technical Data Watch Video Polyester strapping

Considering all of the above, polyester strapping has become a wise choice as a steel strapping replacement.

Production takes place round the clock in Clipsico pack production centers. Highly qualified teams of specialists manufacture Clipsico products satisfying the highest demands of quality on computer-controlled machines.

cilpsicopack

offers wide range of high performance stretch wrap

request an inquiry The Advantages

The Clipsico pack Polyester Strapping offers excellent mechanical features such as high breaking strength, outstanding elongation, and perfect tension retaining capabilities.

These characteristics result in:
  • No damage or contamination of packaging goods (Corrosion-resistant).
  • High shock absorption in case of impacts during transportation.
  • Less pressure on edges of packages (Corner Protectors often not needed).
  • Reduction of material costs (up to 50% savings).
  • Less risk of injury in case of strapping breakages.
  • Perfect on individually secured packages.
  • Strap tension remains tight in cases where the package may shrink during storage or transportation.
  • Substitution of steel strapping by STARstrap™ Polyester allows the use of strapping with less breaking strength.
  • Easy and clean handling compared to steel strapping (recyclable).

item.title: Word of CEO
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
Explore Ourword of ceo

Clipsico Pack’s long term vision is to become the leading manufacturer and supplier of packaging and wrapping solutions. Our excellence in operation, which is based on quality, is what defines our production process. We incorporate quality into our production in order to generate project and product excellence. We strive to exceed customers’ expectations and meet the variations in their demands.

As a socially and environmentally responsible PP (Polypropylene) strap & LLDPE (Linear Low Density Polyethylene) stretch film manufacturer, we are committed to provide high quality products and conduct our manufacturing operations within the prescribed environmental policies and guidelines. We advocate for a safer environment at the work place to reduce hazardous and accidental rates.

With a solid foundation and a visionary management, we are highly-motivated to produce sustainable packaging solutions. As the packaging industry will relentlessly grow, we will continue upgrading our products with smart shapes, space saving packaging, reduction in packaging materials, better recycling and biodegradable packaging

We are an organized, innovative and trustworthy packaging partner. Our position cannot be easily attained without the dedicated hard work and teamwork collaboration among our customers, employees and business partners. With the dedication and experience of our people we will continue to grow and successfully achieve our goals. item.title: How to distinguish PE stretch film quality?
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
PE stretch film is the most commonly used in the industry, a protective film material, which can be single or tray packaging and other bundles, PE stretch film the use of needs to have good transparency, so when we are in the test, You can take transparent plastic transmittance and haze test methods.

There are several ways to identify the PE stretch film

First Measurement

  • The stretchable range of PE stretch film

The stretchable range is the stretch that can be applied while various properties in the case of certain use.
the larger the stretchable range the lower the amount of film used and thus the lower the film cost.

request an inquiry

Second Measurement

  • Stretching of PE stretch film

Stretching of PE stretch film is the ability of a film to produce elastic elongation after being subjected to tension. Stretching will thin the film and shorter the width.

Third Measurement

  • The toughness of PE stretch film

The ability of the film to stretch around corners of products, boxes, and pallets allows increase puncture and tear resistance. This increased puncture resistance ensures loads will remain stabilized and secure during transportation.

The tear resistance means the ability of tear resistance of the film after being subjected to tension and being punctured.

Thus the better the toughness of PE stretch film the better the quality.

fourth Measurement

  • The self adhesiveness of PE stretch film

It means the adhesion between the film layers after contact, during, and after stretching and wrapping.

for a better quality of self, adhesion film is that it should be glossy film, and to use fillers that increase adhesion to make the surface of the film moist thereby improving adhesion.

item.title: Polyester Strapping
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
Storage and Transport

Affect your goods in various ways. Vibrations, temperature differences, and sunlight may have a negative impact on pallet strapping material and cause packaging to become unstable. In order to cope with such challenges, we have developed a vast portfolio of different polyester straps. Today, PET STRAP (POLYESTER STRAP) is recognized as a new environment protective strapping material to substitute Steel Strap. request an inquiry

PP Strap

Since it has the absolute advantages than other products, such as Better Pull Resistance, Superior Elasticity, Low Creep (Extension), Better Temperature Resistance, Excellent Rusty Resistance, Alternative Colors, Easier Operation, Extreme Safety, And Economy, etc.

PET Straps

Are widely used in many different branches of industry, such as an industry, steel industry, architecture materials binding, chemical fiber industry, paper plants, glass industrial, agriculture, tobacco, electronics, and so forth.

Our Polyester

Strapping selection contains numerous types of strapping. These Hand Grade Strapping, Machine Grade Strapping, and Signode Comparable Strapping are suitable for meeting various types of strapping needs.

item.title: Hand Grade Stretch Film
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
Stretch film

Designed specifically to be applied manually is referred to as hand stretch film. It is also referred to as hand film, hand stretch wrap, hand wrap, or manual pallet wrap. It is typically utilized in lower volume packaging operations. However, the efficiency of manual stretch wrap packaging should be regularly re-evaluated against the potential benefits of upgrading to machine-applied films.

We offer an ideal quality hand-grade stretch film that fulfills all kinds of requirements of packages finely.

It is proven best for strength. It is easy and fast to wrap and offers a very fine grip.

We offer a wide range of hand-grade stretch films with varied thicknesses. It is available with normal to heavy-duty packaging. For broad-spectrum use, it is available with 12 microns, also available up to 50-micron film. It offers full safety to heavy loads and there is no need to proceed for an extra layer.

item.title: How To Save Stretch Wrapping Film Cost?
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
1. Downgauging Stretch Film

To downgauge a film means to make the film thinner.

Less material is used in the process, and this can help a lot of companies meet their goals to reduce the amount of packaging material they use.

Financially, downgauging 5% leads to a 5% reduction in material cost.

By downgauging companies can save a tremendous amount of money per pallet.

request an inquiry

2. Pre-stretch-able Film

Using Pre-stretch-able wrapping film can save money because of its high stability, intense physical energy.

This type of film allows the stretching to reach near its breaking point and by doing so, creates a substantial amount of additional lengths to the usable film into the process. This pre-stretching process is not possible by a human, and can only be done with a specific type of wrapping machine.

Common pre-stretch percentages range from 150-300%

That means that every meter of the film coming off a roll represents 2.5 to 4 meters of the film on the load.

There are definitely more ways to introduce savings into the packaging operation and these are just some standard methods that can be implemented right away to your company.

Typically, a company that wraps a significant amount of pallets a day is much more worth moving into machinery wrapping as it will not only saves on the film usage with pre-stretching it but also on the labor usage.

If you are still unsure if your company fits into the downgauging or machine wrapping category, give us a call or drop us an email.

Our packaging experts will guide you through our complete range of packaging solutions.

item.title: Different Types of Stretch Film
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
Because one-size-fits-all solutions rarely work,

Stretch film is offered in an array of types, sizes, formulations, and thicknesses. Some of the most common types of stretch film are :

1-Machine Stretch Film

  • As the name suggests, machine stretch film is designed to be applied by a machine. It offers several advantages over hand stretch film including efficiency, safety, speed, and lower materials cost. At the same time, machine stretch film leads to more secure loads.

2-Hand Stretch Film

  • Hand stretch film, in contrast to machine stretch film, is designed to be applied by hand. This type of film is regularly used in smaller capacity operations. While hand stretch film may not offer the efficiency, speed, and scale of machine stretch, it’s an attractive option if you’re looking to avoid the capital expense of a stretch film machine.

item.title: PCR /PIR Stretch Film
item.dc:creator: clipsicopack_dev
item.content:encoded:
Eco-Friendly Packaging

Recently, there has been a lot of discussion about environmental challenges and recycling of packaging materials, which lead Clipsicopack to fulfil their customers sustainability goals. Offering environmentally friendly and sustainable packaging for excellent product protection include recycled materials from 30% up to 70% with the same performance as the conventional stretch film which includes 100% LLDPE polyethene. Powered by an Aenor certificate, that helps our customers in applying their governmental laws and regulations, promote, waste reuse reduce carbon footprint, and more positive impact on our earth, available in pre-stretch, rigid, coloured & UV stretch film

As we would like to merge the efficiency in our operation and awareness of our target market’s values and preferences, Clipsicopack R& D department with the assistance of our partner ExxonMobil take firm steps toward the recycling track through many trials on the new production line that delivered impressive results. These results come with a stretch film of up to 70% combination of both post-consumer & post-industrial recycled materials with high-standard performance.

Other available stretch film types

Clipsicopack work hard to ensure every product is sustainable as possible. Join us on our sustainable journey and consider joining the European plastic act. To learn more about our recycle stretch film and sustainable innovations, we are available all the time to  contact us

  • Pre-stretch film.
  • Rigid stretch film.
  • Colored Stretch film.
  • UVI stretch film.
  • Biodegradable stretch film .

*All products can be done with 100% virgin material or with the percentage of PCR required .
